    "labels": [],
    "description": "Description: As a new user, I want to create an account by providing my personal details (username, email, password, etc.) so that I can access the application with secure credentials.\nAcceptance Criteria\n- Successful Account Creation\n- Given valid input (username, email, password)\n- When the user submits the form\n- Then the system should create the account and return a success message.\n- Mandatory Fields Validation\n- If any required field is missing, the system should display an error message.\n- Unique Constraints\n- If the email or username already exists, the system should prevent creation and show \"User already exists\".\n- Password Policy Enforcement\n- Password must be at least 8 characters, contain 1 uppercase, 1 number, and 1 special character.\n- Email Format Validation\n- Invalid email formats should be rejected with \"Invalid email format\".\n- Default Role Assignment\n- If no role is specified, assign \"user\" by default.\n- Audit Logging\n- Log account creation events with user ID, timestamp, and origin.",
